window.bookSummaryJSON = "<p>Now a <i>USA Today</i> best-seller.</p> <p>What do you do when you discover your super-hot blind date from months ago is now your super-hot Russian lit professor? You overthink everything and pray for a swift end to your misery, of course!&nbsp;</p> <p><i>Kissing Tolstoy</i> is the first audiobook in the Dear Professor series, and it can be listened to as a stand-alone. A shorter version of this story was entitled \"Nobody Looks Good in Leather Pants\" and was available via Penny Reid's newsletter for free over the course of 2017.</p>"; 
